      • createActivityFromCoord

        Activity createActivityFromCoord(String actType,
                                 Coord coord)
        Creates an Activity from a coordinate. Such activities are assigned to a link on running the Controler.
        Parameters:
        actType - - the type of the activity, which needs to correspond to some string in the config file
        coord - - the coordinates of the activity
        Returns:
        the activity

        It might in fact make sense to add a creational method that takes coord and link id. kai, aug'10

      • createActivityFromLinkId

        Activity createActivityFromLinkId(String actType,
                                  Id<Link> linkId)
        Creates an Activity from a link id. No coordinate will be associated directly with this activity. This does not add the activity into the plan.
        Parameters:
        actType - - the type of the activity, which needs to correspond to some string in the config file
        Returns:
        the activity
